It’s the climax, people. Big stuff’s gonna happen April 8 on Prime.

snippet.description:
After the LAW's 1000 player army was slaughtered by Wemmbu and Flame, their leader, LettuceK held an emergency announcement... where he announced that he would be holding an election for King of Unstable. This is Unstable SMP: The First King. 

Like ParrotX2 and his Unstable SMP series, where he is escaping Paragon / Proton: Minecraft's Most Secure Prison, or got hunted by a Minecraft Player who doesn't exist. This is a new and original Minecraft idea like HermitCraft or Lifesteal with Wemmbu, FlameFrags, or Spoke. Survival is harder than Hardcore Minecraft because PVP is on.

Knight Of The Seven Kingdoms Trailer https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Thfoq8GqcY&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxGuSDE8NtOuthqbKFChC0q&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
The Legend Of Zelda Movie Teaser Trailer https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iL4iNuc3sz0&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
Spider-Man Brand New Day Trailer https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B_59lBNjosE&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
Emergency Awesome New Videos https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeOfhzu7ZdY&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=7

Covering Supergirl Teaser Trailer 2026. Milly Alcock Supergirl from House of the Dragon, Jason Momoa Lobo Returns, Superman Movie Aftermath, Peacemaker Season 2 DCU Timeline, Superman Timeline. Superman 2 Man of Tomorrow Crossover with Brainiac.

Netflix Warner Bros Announcement. Netflix announced it was buying Warner Brothers. What that means for James Gunn future DC Movies, future TV Shows like Superman 2 Man of Tomorrow, Green Lantern, Batman Brave & The Bold, the new Justice League Movie & everything else. House Of the Dragon Season 3, the new Harry Potter Series 2027. What Netflix is changing and what isn't changing.

I recently got to speak directly with James Gunn one on one. I was surprised he was a fan of my Emergency Awesome videos. We talked about the future of the DCU, upcoming movies and tv shows from Superman 2 Man of Tomorrow Teasers,  Lanterns, New Gods Darkseid and Mr Miracle TV Show, Justice League, Batman, The Flash and the Supergirl Movie. There was a lot! We even talked about Game Of Thrones & George RR Martin.

Peacemaker Season 2 Episode 8 Ending. Superman Easter Eggs. James Gunn new Justice League. Fortress Of Solitude, Bradley Cooper Jor-El Cameo Scene, Kelex Robots, New Scenes. New Batman Changes and DC Movies Plan for Batman Explained. New Footage and Scenes. Fortress of Solitude. Superman vs Ultraman, Evil Superman. Green Lantern First Look. Mr Terrific Krypto Scene. Letra : 
Vengo de la nada
pero eh venido por todo
me toco ser oveja 
también me toco ser lobo
lo que si les juro
esque no me vuelvo a caer

y que no les duela 
Cuando el loco este en la cima
esta va por el angel 
que me cuida desde arriba
se que estará orgulloso 
de qué porfin lo logre

la que vive en mi casa 
esa se llama familia
los demás son parientes
y algunos son pura envidia
no siempre la sangre
es la que te quiere ver bien

hablan de mi sin saber 
sin saber que me vale verga 
lo que digan lo que hagan y lo que dejen de hacer 

la suerte son los huevos
que le pongas a la vida
la clave es la paciencia
roma no se hizo en un día
cosas tan sencillas
que no lograba entender 

se quebró la piñata
de tanto que le pegamos
los que nomas miraban
en caliente se aventaron
fueron los primeros
doble cara que aleje
y ahora hablan de mi sin saber 
sin saber que me vale verga 
lo que digan lo que hagan y lo que dejen de hacer
